Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.40,0:01:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角色扮演七变化高潮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.41,0:01:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(现代影视文化研究会)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.43,0:01:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了就受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美你可以做那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.44,0:01:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.37,0:01:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个  好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美  我想看  真的好想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美  拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.39,0:02:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就来做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.40,0:02:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美好可爱\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.41,0:02:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们社团举办的见面会一定来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太刺激了\N我要昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N小乃美被盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们才能保护吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.38,0:03:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不允许别人来污辱小乃美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.45,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美加入这个社团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.39,0:03:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家在一起真的好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.46,0:03:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美\N你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家对不起\N乃美太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.48,0:03:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.41,0:03:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N大家要让见面会成功哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.49,0:03:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美也会努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.43,0:03:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今天就解散吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.38,0:04:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天放学后准时在这集合好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.39,0:04:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.46,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解\N我会处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几分钟后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了  松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.44,0:05:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  任性的说想跟你独处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  只要是你的请求我都愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松好温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.45,0:05:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做你的女朋友一定很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.39,0:05:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N我带了你要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个难道是我想要的那套服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.47,0:05:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美一直很喜欢这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.41,0:05:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢  你喜欢就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要送我吗   好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.49,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美不拆开看看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不知道该怎么感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了...不用感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.38,0:06:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以当做回礼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是亲亲抱抱的意思吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以坐在沙发上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松...可以再亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.48,0:08:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.37,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松...你会讨厌跟我见接吻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.37,0:08:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会  我很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.37,0:08:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你亲的好下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.40,0:09:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身体哪里最舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头\N乳头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.43,0:09:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可以摸吗\N可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.39,0:09:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢怎么被我摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.39,0:10:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手指轻轻弹\N轻轻弹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 你变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.49,0:10:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用捏的  好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.44,0:10:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用舔的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔吗\N可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服\N舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.37,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我舔的舒服吗\N舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.46,0:12:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的回礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.37,0:12:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.46,0:13:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以摸我的肉棒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.48,0:13:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的好棒\N因为很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.42,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒好棒  又大又硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.37,0:14:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边亲边弄会变更硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.44,0:14:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边亲边弄吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.41,0:14:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  变的好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.44,0:15:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美想舔你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.46,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以舔吗\N当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒舒服吗\N舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.49,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒又变的更大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.38,0:17:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.43,0:18:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样感觉可以吗\N很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.46,0:18:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想射给妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.47,0:18:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射多一点哦\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.37,0:19:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射多一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.44,0:19:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.46,0:19:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手太舒服了\N我射了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.47,0:20:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松  我来帮你舔干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.42,0:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好敏一感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痒痒的吗\N很痒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.38,0:20:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射谢你的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.45,0:21:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.46,0:21:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好保存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.47,0:21:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒\N你家好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.41,0:21:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害\N住这么好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.42,0:21:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸为了方便我上学...买了小套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.49,0:21:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美是第一个来这的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.37,0:21:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.37,0:21:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想看你收藏的经典DVD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.45,0:22:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个也不难拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.38,0:22:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先预购就有赠送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.39,0:22:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.40,0:22:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美能跟你认识真的太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.41,0:22:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N我进男生的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.48,0:22:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.49,0:22:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.49,0:22:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我不是为了想看DVD来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.43,0:22:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.43,0:22:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是因为想来你家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.37,0:22:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才用想看影片当藉囗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.44,0:23:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会讨厌我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.38,0:23:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.45,0:24:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多亲我一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.42,0:24:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想亲小乃美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.43,0:24:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.37,0:25:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美   真的可以吗\N可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.45,0:25:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太用力了\N抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.40,0:25:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可以吸我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.45,0:26:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   摸胸部会很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.48,0:27:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看我的胸部吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.42,0:27:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就破例给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.39,0:27:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的胸部软吗  松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.46,0:27:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.40,0:27:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.49,0:28:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:19.43,0:28:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.37,0:28:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗\N帮我解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:54.40,0:28:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头好小好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.40,0:29:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:04.41,0:29:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.41,0:29:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢的都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.49,0:29:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.37,0:29:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:03.40,0:30:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松  你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.47,0:30:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你摸这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.43,0:30:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.44,0:30:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.37,0:30:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.38,0:30:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样摸吗\N就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:01.46,0:31:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很害羞  可以拿掉眼镜吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:06.40,0:31:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.49,0:31:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里最舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.49,0:31:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服\N这吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.44,0:31:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看里面吗\N里面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.44,0:31:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.47,0:32:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.41,0:32:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:33.42,0:32:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:39.42,0:32:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以摸吗\N可以摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.37,0:32:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要摸哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.37,0:32:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:58.37,0:33:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.44,0:33:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗\N很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.46,0:33:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美  你湿湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.40,0:33:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你摸了就会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.40,0:33:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.42,0:33:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.37,0:34:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进两根了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.40,0:34:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.48,0:34:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.49,0:34:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:59.43,0:35:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样插吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.37,0:35:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再弄快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.47,0:35:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了  不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:07.50,0:36:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿湿的流出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.45,0:36:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松  好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:27.38,0:36:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.49,0:37:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松   这么激烈不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.45,0:37:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.37,0:38:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好舒服\N这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.42,0:39:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松  不能太刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:00.40,0:40:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以摸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.47,0:40:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你脱掉裤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.39,0:41:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这里变的好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.48,0:41:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以直接看一吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.49,0:41:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内裤脱掉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.44,0:41:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要摸我的吗\N我想摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.39,0:42:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢我怎么弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.40,0:42:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很舒服\N这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.40,0:42:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过能弄一点口水吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.48,0:42:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口水?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.42,0:42:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.43,0:42:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.50,0:42:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:02.44,0:43:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的逼越来越热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.47,0:43:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不舔我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:36.48,0:43:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我舔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.39,0:44:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗\N舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:36.41,0:44:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起舔好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:39.48,0:44:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.48,0:44:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.43,0:46:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉...这样我舔不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:17.44,0:46:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服舔不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:33.46,0:46:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:57.48,0:47:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松  我也受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:04.42,0:47:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.50,0:47:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以插进去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:19.37,0:47:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松  我们合为一体吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:25.37,0:47:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:53.40,0:47:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.42,0:48:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:28.37,0:48:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的很硬很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:33.44,0:48:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:57.47,0:49:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:47.38,0:49:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太猛了不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:56.45,0:51:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒  好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:58.45,0:52:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽插看的好清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:07.39,0:52:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:17.40,0:52:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再插深一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:13.46,0:53:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:19.46,0:53:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服\N我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:44.42,0:53:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:46.42,0:53:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美的小穴舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:51.49,0:53:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:09.38,0:54:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再高潮没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:39.41,0:54:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:48.41,0:55:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:51.48,0:55:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以再来找你玩吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:55.48,0:55:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:58.42,0:56:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:13.37,0:56:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:19.37,0:56:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱 好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:22.44,0:56:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒  这样超可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:33.39,0:56:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:36.46,0:56:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再换一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:44.47,0:56:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒  可以往下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:53.41,0:56:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:01.42,0:57:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再笑一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:13.43,0:57:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再低一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:16.50,0:57:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美  转过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:22.37,0:57:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱  这个好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:30.38,0:57:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美转过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:39.46,0:57:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也要  好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:49.47,0:57:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这来  来个爱心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:00.41,0:58:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美   这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:08.42,0:58:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要爱心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:11.49,0:58:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美你看   这张不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:14.42,0:58:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶  你好会拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:18.43,0:58:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太会摆姿势了\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:23.50,0:58:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:25.50,0:58:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这张   好看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:28.44,0:58:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍的也好棒\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:32.44,0:58:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的不是专业摄影师吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:36.45,0:58:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好棒\N你看这张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:40.45,0:58:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张也好棒\N把我拍的好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:44.45,0:58:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:46.46,0:58:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍的好可爱\N这张也很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:51.39,0:58:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:59.40,0:59:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么了\N没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:07.41,0:59:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:09.41,0:59:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像变硬了\N没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:18.49,0:59:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你们是因为我兴奋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:25.43,0:59:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.43,0:59:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:31.43,0:59:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:34.37,0:59:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这里\N有点想看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:42.38,0:59:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N我想看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:46.38,0:59:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会害羞\N是真吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:51.45,0:59:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:54.39,0:59:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你这么说\N那就脱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:09.47,1:00:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都变大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.41,1:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的还行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:18.41,1:00:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:21.48,1:00:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个还会变更大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.42,1:00:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.42,1:00:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看更大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:32.43,1:00:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:39.37,1:00:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就会变大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:48.44,1:00:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美  能看你的腋下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.38,1:00:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腋下\N会变更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:54.45,1:00:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗   好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:06.46,1:01:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太近了会受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:12.47,1:01:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:13.40,1:01:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  变的好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:23.41,1:01:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以靠近看吗\N可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:28.48,1:01:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们脱掉好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:37.43,1:01:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒...变大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:49.44,1:01:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不懂...我摸会更大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:55.44,1:01:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的   你摸\N可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:10.39,1:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们舒服吗\N很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:16.40,1:02:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做才会变更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:21.47,1:02:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快一点\N快一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:23.47,1:02:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:27.48,1:02:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的嘴巴还会再变大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:31.48,1:02:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的嘴巴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:35.48,1:02:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:49.50,1:02:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是弄错了\N是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.38,1:03:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头头好像湿湿的\N抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:12.45,1:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:23.40,1:03:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒   可以再深一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:27.40,1:03:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮流来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:37.41,1:03:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样两个人不大好弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:41.42,1:03:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个一个舒服好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:44.49,1:03:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:53.43,1:03:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢怎么玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:59.44,1:04:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你亲亲\N亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:05.44,1:04:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:11.45,1:04:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲亲会变更大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:24.39,1:04:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再舔一下好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:46.42,1:04:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗\N你最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:09.37,1:05:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吸你的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:28.46,1:05:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你舔的好猛\N你也舔我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:40.47,1:05:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:48.48,1:05:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗\N你最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:52.48,1:05:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:58.49,1:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比刚刚还硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:03.43,1:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃你的口水会更硬\N口水吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:20.38,1:06:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗?\N好吃  再给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:23.45,1:06:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:34.39,1:06:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:37.46,1:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:44.40,1:06:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒也要口水
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:00.42,1:07:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多一点\N多一点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:11.49,1:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多弄一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:22.44,1:07:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:36.45,1:07:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再含深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:41.39,1:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒   这样好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:07.42,1:08:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:09.42,1:08:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后会射东西出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:17.43,1:08:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要我怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:19.43,1:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一边舔一边帮我手淫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:23.43,1:08:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:57.47,1:09:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想射吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:18.42,1:09:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射多一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:59.39,1:10:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:16.48,1:10:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部射出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:29.42,1:10:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:36.50,1:10:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:49.45,1:10:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你射的真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:52.38,1:10:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉弄脏你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:00.39,1:11:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你舔干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:29.49,1:11:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也要把我拍的很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:37.49,1:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱   谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:40.43,1:11:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让妳久等了\N没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:44.43,1:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢怎么做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:50.44,1:11:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你亲亲\N亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.44,1:11:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N我也想亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:02.45,1:12:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:06.46,1:12:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:16.47,1:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸我的舌头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:25.41,1:12:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么喜欢跟我接吻吗\N喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:41.42,1:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸我的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:49.43,1:12:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这里变的好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:53.44,1:12:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为跟你接吻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:59.44,1:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:02.38,1:13:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用口水和手\N帮我手淫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:06.38,1:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:11.45,1:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗\N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.40,1:13:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越热了.\N好下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:46.42,1:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一下下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:55.50,1:13:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就会射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:00.44,1:14:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想放进乃美的嘴里射
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:07.38,1:14:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗\N可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:37.41,1:14:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗\N很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:03.43,1:15:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:41.47,1:15:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以射吗\N请射出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:31.39,1:16:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再口交快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:37.39,1:16:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:45.40,1:16:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  掉出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:55.41,1:16:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然好用力\N抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:00.48,1:17:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜甜的\N抱歉弄脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:05.42,1:17:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太舒服就忍不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:09.42,1:17:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:13.43,1:17:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你舔干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:01.48,1:18:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也要帮我拍的很可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:05.48,1:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定\N谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:21.50,1:18:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好  我是乃美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:26.44,1:18:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样好看吗  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:37.38,1:18:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看我胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:40.45,1:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   今天不能那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:43.39,1:18:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有新的打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:46.46,1:18:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想给大家看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:50.46,1:18:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能做禁播的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:56.47,1:18:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:03.41,1:19:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱吗  我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:14.48,1:19:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做给我看\N不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:20.49,1:19:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发颜色不好看\N啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:28.50,1:19:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:31.43,1:19:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打扮的是\N可爱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:34.37,1:19:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:36.37,1:19:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上次你们指定的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:43.45,1:19:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想表演自慰感谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:49.45,1:19:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:54.39,1:19:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到我了  冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:59.46,1:20:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:01.46,1:20:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望大家也能爽一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:05.47,1:20:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:08.40,1:20:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:26.42,1:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到画面啦\N冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:33.50,1:20:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样   有看到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:36.43,1:20:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看的到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:41.37,1:20:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:05.39,1:21:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我的内裤吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:22.48,1:21:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  想不想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:25.41,1:21:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃美的性感带
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:33.42,1:21:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:44.50,1:21:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样  摸这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:51.44,1:21:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突突的地方会很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:05.45,1:22:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有点舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:18.40,1:22:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要看好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:01.38,1:23:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:12.45,1:23:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也在手淫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:20.46,1:23:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很硬的话就跟我一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:48.49,1:23:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:50.49,1:23:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手越来越快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:08.38,1:24:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看胸部吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:11.45,1:24:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真的很爱看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:16.39,1:24:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么喜欢看胸部吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:24.39,1:24:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:33.47,1:24:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:45.48,1:24:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道很小\N不要嫌弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:54.42,1:24:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸这里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:01.50,1:25:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就越来越舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:07.50,1:25:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:11.37,1:25:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:19.38,1:25:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头硬了   很舒服就会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:34.46,1:25:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我喜欢用点力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:41.40,1:25:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不被动型   是主动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:52.48,1:25:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有很用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:57.42,1:26:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力道很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:10.50,1:26:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想靠近点看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:15.44,1:26:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:35.46,1:26:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头很硬吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:40.40,1:26:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:51.47,1:26:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想看胸部了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:58.41,1:27:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换内裤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:02.42,1:27:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面也想看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:14.43,1:27:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先脱内裤好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:44.46,1:27:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是看不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:49.40,1:27:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:54.47,1:27:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看内裤吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:04.48,1:28:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我穿的内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:25.43,1:28:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继缆啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:37.45,1:28:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:44.39,1:28:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸摸看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:53.46,1:28:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:02.40,1:29:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:08.41,1:29:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想听声音吗?  怎么弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:23.49,1:29:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有听到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:39.37,1:29:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很湿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:48.45,1:29:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最舒服的地方是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:03.40,1:30:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:13.41,1:30:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:41.44,1:30:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:59.46,1:31:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服都忘了直播
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:29.49,1:31:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么也该
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:33.49,1:31:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用大家最想看的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:37.49,1:31:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:40.43,1:31:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最爱用的就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:48.44,1:31:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:31.41,1:32:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:37.42,1:32:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:43.43,1:32:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:50.50,1:32:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都自慰吗?  没有每天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:54.50,1:32:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:00.38,1:33:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我都用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:10.39,1:33:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看再强一点的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:17.46,1:33:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太强的话会很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:28.40,1:33:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢激烈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:26.46,1:34:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快要去了  大家也准备好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:32.47,1:34:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:36.47,1:34:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:01.43,1:35:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:05.43,1:35:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一起去吗   那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:14.38,1:35:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就播放到这里  谢谢观看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:23.45,1:35:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也要收看好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:27.46,1:35:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:33.46,1:35:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很舒服  再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:43.47,1:35:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿仲你真的有看到播出吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:50.41,1:35:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉乃美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:53.48,1:35:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久以前就知道是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:59.49,1:36:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:03.49,1:36:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了昨天的直播
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:07.50,1:36:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到其他人也看到就很...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:12.43,1:36:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下流的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:17.37,1:36:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得被其他看到很不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:23.38,1:36:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:26.45,1:36:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会被对手的社团利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:34.46,1:36:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我觉得有点太危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:38.46,1:36:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么可爱的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:42.46,1:36:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就这样白白被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:49.40,1:36:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为了你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:55.41,1:36:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:58.48,1:37:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿仲  谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:00.48,1:37:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么担心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:03.42,1:37:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿仲   你不会告诉别人对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:11.43,1:37:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会跟大家说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:14.50,1:37:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  阿仲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:24.37,1:37:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:26.38,1:37:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护乃美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:31.45,1:37:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:34.38,1:37:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会把乃美的事情泄漏出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:48.40,1:37:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:50.40,1:37:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会保护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:55.47,1:37:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:58.41,1:38:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我应该要好好谢谢你的才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:05.48,1:38:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:35.38,1:38:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到真的能跟你这这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:39.38,1:38:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是特例
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:43.39,1:38:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次到男生家里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:53.40,1:38:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在忙   交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:58.47,1:39:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先挂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:06.48,1:39:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护乃美
